reviewText: This movie was vulgar and I would not watch it again. I wish I had not watched it once. I would definitely not let children watch this movie.
Interesting premise, poorly executed. The pacing of the movie is too slow for an action film.
Such a fun movie! Classic coming of age video.
All around fun movie. I mean really, what kid has not dreamed of having super powers! I wish I was max! save the world and get the girl!
